' Shared legend block — embedded at the bottom of diagrams that
' display routing/characterization vocabulary (rung / prior / scheme).

legend right
  | symbol | meaning |
  | <#FFFFFF>**rung** | real staircase climb (passes recorded) |
  | <#FFFDF6>**prior** | low-confidence QCM/branch prior (Dyy/D12 discount) |
  | <#E6DFD2>**none** | never measured (D8.B: leave blank, never zero) |
  | scheme | `beta-laplace-v1` (current) or `breaking-rung-v0` (legacy) |
endlegend
